reviewText: So old a lot of the information is not longer current. You're better off just using Wikipedia. I'm not even joking.

I guess its information is ok. I own tattoo shop and we have always been known for our work and marketing ideas. But sun sun block block just is so stupid. It doesn't really explain how to hit said people as much as it explains the ways in which your brand can be effective to said people.  In my case I know what my people want just not how to get them to see me. I have north Chicago's locked down but west and south I am struggling.

It definitely helps you understand the concepts of finance. I got hooked on these back in high school. I still think they're rather relevant. The presentation is a bit on the... strange side. It's the strangeness that makes it stick for you.
